| `analyzePairAndTradeWithCandles` (ln 4046) | candle | (usa seأ±al previa) | (evaluado arriba) | âœ… ln 4917 |
| `analyzePairAndTrade` (ln 3037) | cycle | â‌Œ | â‌Œ (previo) | âœ… ln 3846 |

