- `server/services/marketMetrics/providers/DeFiLlamaProvider.ts` â€” Suministro/contracciأ³n de stablecoins (gratis, sin API key)
- `server/services/marketMetrics/providers/CoinMetricsProvider.ts` â€” Flujos netos hacia exchanges (gratis con lأ­mites)
- `server/services/marketMetrics/providers/WhaleAlertProvider.ts` â€” Inflow de ballenas a exchanges (requiere `WHALE_ALERT_API_KEY`)
- `server/services/marketMetrics/providers/CoinGlassProvider.ts` â€” Open Interest, Funding Rate, Liquidaciones (requiere `COINGLASS_API_KEY`)

#### FASE 3: Migraciأ³n DB
